CommonWriterUtils
public class NestedWriterSF
extends java.lang.Object
implements CommonWriterUtils

Implementation for a nested writer that uses a SequenceFile as output. It implements the outlines of the CommonWriterUtils interface.

Author:
Daniel Stanoescu
